<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>byy trktk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 byy trktk rḥt bʿyd wnkrtk
 wbhạlḥẓh tdẖkrtk sạmḥny ạ̹sẖtqtlk
 ạ̉ṣḥạby trkwny ạ̹ftkrtn yḥbwny
 bḍʿfy ạ̹zywny trkwny wḥyd
 yạ byy ạlḥnwn yạ byy ạlrḥwm wʿdk mạ byzwl yạ byy
 ạgẖmrny bḥnạnk ʿysẖy bslạmk qwyny bklạmk
 rạjʿ lʿnk ạ̉kyd. tʿṭyny ḥnạn mn jdyd
 btshr ʿly ʿṭwl yạ byy ạlwḥyd
 rạjʿ lʿndk tʿbạn ʿm fkr wḥdy fzʿạn
 tsẖkr ạ̉w tftḥly ạlbạb sẖw rḥ ykwn ạljwạb
 kẖṭyt bḥqk byy sạmḥny wmạ bstạhl klmẗ yạ ạ̹bny
 wbsrʿẗ sẖftk jạyy lʿndy wbạ̉ʿly̱
 ṣwtk tṣrkẖ wtqly
 yạ ạ̉bny msẖtạq tḍmk bqlby ʿywny
 frḥạny tbky dmwʿ
 kl lyly nạṭr .nạṭr trjʿly rḥ tbqy̱ ạ̹bnyʿly̱ ṭwl
 tdẖkr ạ̹ny bḥbk.ạ̉nạ byk ʿṭwl bḥbk</lyrics>
